Package: IHWpaper
Title: Reproduce figures in IHW paper
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("Nikos", "Ignatiadis", email = "nikos.ignatiadis01@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package conveniently wraps all functions needed to 
        reproduce the figures in the IHW preprint, available on biorXiv
        under http://biorxiv.org/content/early/2016/03/30/034330.
        Thus it is a companion package to the Bioconductor IHW package.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3),
    IHW,
    fdrtool,
    genefilter,
    DESeq,
    DESeq2,
    FDRreg,
    qvalue,
    Biobase,
    BiocGenerics,
    BiocParallel,
    dplyr,
    cowplot,
    airway,
    pasilla,
    gridExtra,
    tidyr,
    RColorBrewer,
    ggplot2,
    wesanderson,
    scales,
    BiocStyle,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports:
    Rcpp
VignetteBuilder: knitr
biocViews:
    ReproducibleResearch
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
